      <title>Carmine Gallo - The Apple Experience</title>
      <link>http://feeds.conversationsnetwork.org/~r/channel/itc/~3/B52ba2d9nJQ/detail5297.html</link>
      <description>Apple has built a successful retail store business that is based on giving customers a unique and positive experience whenever they enter the store. Carmine Gallo describes how other businesses can take advantage of the Soul of Apple to develop service strategies that will make them more profitable by considering every aspect of their customers and their needs.&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
